#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:804
msgid ""
"enter the table name in :config:option:`$cfg['Servers'][$i]['bookmarktable']`"
msgstr ""
"укажите имя таблицы в :config:option:`$cfg['Servers'][$i]['bookmarktable']`"

#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:806 ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:843
#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:872 ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:984
#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:1021 ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:1047
#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:1077 ../phpmyadmin/docs/config.rst:1099
