"an open-source, cross-platform data compression library by `Jean-loup Gailly "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Loup_Gailly>`_ and `Mark Adler <https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_Adler>`_."
