#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/setup.rst:422
msgid ":config:option:`$cfg['Servers'][$i]['SessionTimeZone']`"
msgstr ":config:option:`$cfg['Servers'][$i]['SessionTimeZone']`"

#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/setup.rst:424
msgid ""
"By default, :ref:`cookie` is used, but if :envvar:`PMA_USER` "
"and :envvar:`PMA_PASSWORD` are set, it is switched to :ref:`auth_config`."
msgstr ""
"По умолчанию используется :ref:`cookie`, но если :envvar:`PMA_USER` и "
":envvar:`PMA_PASSWORD` заданы, происходит переключение на :ref:`auth_config`."

#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/setup.rst:429
msgid ""
"The credentials you need to log in are stored in the MySQL server, in case "
"of Docker image, there are various ways to set it (for "
"example :samp:`MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD` when starting the MySQL container). "
"Please check documentation for `MariaDB container <https://hub.docker.com/_/"
"mariadb>`_ or `MySQL container <https://hub.docker.com/_/mysql>`_."
msgstr ""
"Учётные данные, необходимые для входа, хранятся на сервере MySQL. В случае "
"образа Docker существуют различные способы их установки (например, "
":samp:`MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD` при запуске контейнера MySQL). Пожалуйста, "
"проверьте документацию для `контейнера MariaDB <https://hub.docker.com/_/"
"mariadb>`_ или `контейнера MySQL <https://hub.docker.com/_/mysql>`_."

#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/setup.rst:438
msgid "Customizing configuration"
msgstr "Настройка конфигурации"

#: ../phpmyadmin/docs/setup.rst:440
msgid ""
"Additionally configuration can be tweaked by :file:`/etc/phpmyadmin/"
"config.user.inc.php`. If this file exists, it will be loaded after "
"configuration is generated from above environment variables, so you can "
"override any configuration variable. This configuration can be added as a "
"volume when invoking docker using `-v /some/local/directory/"
"config.user.inc.php:/etc/phpmyadmin/config.user.inc.php` parameters."
msgstr ""
